name: Symbiosis (itch) (lFalconl)
description:
Ever wanted a platformer with a tonk? No? Ok but here it is anyway

Use A and D to move around, space or W to jump. Press M to turn off music.

Collect the blue thingies and deposit them in the tank to progress.

Music is by Context Sensitive: "Anode" here's a link to his yt channel
